# Copy to `.dev.vars` in this directory (`apps/api/.dev.vars`).
# Wrangler loads `.dev.vars` for `wrangler dev` only. The real file is gitignored — never commit secrets.
#
# See README.md → "Secrets vs configuration" for what belongs here vs `wrangler secret` in production.

# --- Brevo (transactional email) ---
# Production / staging: use `wrangler secret put BREVO_API_KEY` (never commit the key).
# BREVO_API_KEY=

# Safe as non-secret (or use [vars] in wrangler.toml / dashboard for prod defaults).
# BREVO_SENDER_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com
# BREVO_SENDER_NAME=Tradebook

# --- Messaging WebSocket tickets (optional override; default also in wrangler [vars] for local) ---
# WEBSOCKET_TICKET_SECRET=

# --- Future (when wired in code) ---
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# BUDGETSMS_API_KEY=
# MAPBOX_SERVER_TOKEN=
